quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Did We not delight/expand your chest (innermost)
  94,2,And We raised from you your sin/load/burden
  94,3,Which weighed heavily (on)/burdened your back
  94,4,And We raised for you your memory/reputation
  94,5,So that truly with the difficulty/hardship (is) ease/flexibility
  94,6,That truly with the difficulty/hardship (is) ease/flexibility
  94,7,"So when/if you finished/ended/completed , so work hard/fatigue"
  94,8,"And to your Lord, so wish/desire"
  95,1,And/by the figs and the olives
  95,2,And/by Seneen Mountain
  95,3,"And/by this the country/land/city , the faithful/secure"
  95,4,We had (E) created the human/mankind in best chronometry/cartography (methods of calculating maps and charts)/straightness (formation)
  95,5,Then We returned him (to) lowest/more lowly/more mean lowly/mean (lowliest)
  95,6,"Except those who believed and made/did the correct/righteous deeds, so for them (is) a not interrupted/weakened reward"
  95,7,So what makes you lie/deny/falsify after with the religion
  95,8,Is God not with (the) most judicious (of) the judges/rulers
  96,1,Read by your Lord`s name who created
  96,2,He created the human/mankind from blood clots/sperm
  96,3,"Read and/by your Lord, the most honoured/generous"
  96,4,Who taught/instructed by the pen/writing utensil
  96,5,He taught/instructed the human/mankind what he did not know
  96,6,No but that truly the human/mankind tyrannizes/exceeds the limit (E)
  96,7,"That (E) he saw/understood him(self), he enriched/sufficed (himself)"
  96,8,That truly to your Lord (is) the return
  96,9,Did you see/understand who forbids/prevents
  96,10,A worshipper/servant/slave when/if he prayed
  96,11,Did you see/understand if he was on the guidance
  96,12,Or he ordered/commanded with the fear and obedience of God
  96,13,Did you see/understand if he lied/denied/falsified and he turned away
  96,14,Does he not know with that (E) God sees/understands
  96,15,"No but if (E) he does not end/terminate/stop, We will pull and strike (E) by the forehead/forehead`s hair"
  96,16,"A lying/denying/falsifying, sinning/erring/wronging forehead/forehead`s hair"
  96,17,So he should call his caller
  96,18,We will call the strong ones/patrol force/Elzabaneya angels
  96,19,"No but do not obey him, and prostrate and near/approach (to Me)"
  97,1,We (E) descended it in the predestined/destiny night
  97,2,And what made you know/informed you what the predestined/destiny night (is)
  97,3,The predestined/destiny night (is) better than one thousand month (lunar months)
  97,4,"The angels descend and the Soul/Spirit in it, by their Lord`s permission/pardon from every matter/affair"
  97,5,Security/peace it is until the dawn`s ascent/rising
  98,1,Those who disbelieved from the Book`s people and the sharers/takers of partners (with God) were not broken to pieces/separated until the evidence comes to them
  98,2,"A messenger from God, he reads/recites/follows purified/cleaned written pages (scriptures)"
  98,3,In it (are) straight/valuable Books
  98,4,And those who were given/brought the Book did not separate except from after what came to them (from) the evidence
  98,5,"And they were not ordered/commanded except to worship God faithful/loyal/devoted to Him (in) the religion (as) submitters/Unifiers of God , and they keep up the prayers, and they give/bring the charity/purification , and that (is) the straight/valuable religion"
  98,6,"That truly those who disbelieved from the Book`s people and the sharers/takers of partners (with God are) in Hell`s fire immortally/eternally in it, those, they are the creation`s worst"
  98,7,"That truly those who believed and made/did the correct/righteous deeds, those, they are the creation`s best"
  98,8,"Their reimbursement (is) at their Lord, treed gardens/paradises (as) eternal residence the rivers/waterways flow from beneath it, immortally/eternally in it (for) ever (E), God accepted/approved on them, and they accepted/approved on Him, that (is) to who feared his Lord"
  99,1,When/if the earth/Planet Earth shook/trembled its shaking/trembling/earthquake
  99,2,And the earth/Planet Earth brought out its loads/weights
  99,3,"And the human/mankind said: \"What (is) for it (what is wrong with it)"
  99,4,That day it tells/informs (about) its news/information/knowledge
  99,5,With that your Lord inspired/transmitted to it
  99,6,"That day, the people proceed/arise separately to see their deeds"
  99,7,So who makes/does a smallest particle of anything (smaller than an atom`s) weight (of) good sees it
  99,8,And who makes/does a smallest particle of anything (smaller than an atom`s) weight (of) bad/evil sees it
  100,1,"And/by the panting/changing colour , attacking forces/horses"
  100,2,"So the igniters (of fire)/swayers , fire striking/sparking/decaying"
  100,3,So the raiders/fast attacking horses (in) mornings/daybreaks
  100,4,So they stirred and arose/agitated dust/splashing mud or water with it
  100,5,So they were in the middle with it all together/(in) a group
  100,6,That truly the human/mankind (is) ungrateful/disobedient (E) to his Lord
  100,7,And he truly (is) on that witnessing/testifying (E)
  100,8,And that he truly to the good`s/wealth`s love/like (is) strong (intense) (E) (humans love excessive goodness)